name: Adut Akech (Model)
description:
Adut Akech Bior is a South Sudanese-Australian model.

This is my first TI model. It is customizable (e.g. hairstyle ) if you use some rather strong weights. See examples.

Big thanks to @JernauGurgeh for the kindness of sharing his amazing process and training settings. Amazing open source spirit, this is why I love this community! Check out his models they are all amazing.
